Date: 1992-04-30

Title: Self-Dual Chern-Simons Solitons in (2+1)-Dimensional Einstein Gravity

Authors: Daniel Cangemi and Choonkyu Lee

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D46 (1992) 4768-4771

We consider here a generalization of the Abelian Higgs model in curved space,by adding a Chern--Simons term. The static equations are self-dual provided wechoose a suitable potential. The solutions give a self-dualMaxwell--Chern--Simons soliton that possesses a mass and a spin.